Create front-end for Employee Web Api with Angular

Requirements:
1. On front-end application load, the app would get employees (firstName, lastName) from .net back-end
2. Be able to add new employee through front-end

Additional requirements:
1 Install Bootstrap to angular and use it to style the form, table
2 Add Delete functionality
3. Add the button which allows to update employee instead of creating.
Use the same form to edit the employee with PUT.